arStrings.szText:
{c_label}Lucky Hit:{/c} Your {c_important}Bone{/c} Skill Critical Strikes have up to a {c_number}[SF_6|%|]{/c} chance to create a pool of blood that deals {c_number}{payload:TOOLTIP_DAMAGE}{/c} damage over {c_number}[SF_1]{/c} seconds. 

While standing in these pools, your {c_important}Blood{/c} Skills:
{icon:bullet,1.2} Gain {c_number}[SF_3 * 100|%+|]{/c} Attack Speed
{icon:bullet,1.2} Gain {c_number}[SF_4 * 100|%x|]{/c} Vulnerable Damage
Blood Skills gain increased Attack Speed and Vulnerable Damage.
